{"tid":1392851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網絡好似出現一個臨時政府咁","createTime":"2019-08-01T01:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T02:45:34.000Z","uid":11779,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"af8138533942a7e00e31cf7be1d47b4475a7340e","tid":1392851,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:23:42.000Z","msg":"612基金：稅收<br />\n連登：議會<br />\n義士：行政<br />\n<br />\n所以港共政府呢幾日不斷抺黑612基金 連我個捐錢post都有3毛出黎搞事帶風向。<br />\n<br />\n港共政權越係抺黑 我地越要企硬！"},{"pid":"bce60a35f87e0affee93ca3e151cc126dad1f36b","tid":1392851,"uid":75156,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:34:30.000Z","msg":"大家好似真係比人洗走左71宣言同臨時立法會既提議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c38f73188f87618b3e793057c89e325a1972a3","tid":1392851,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:49:03.000Z","msg":"認真要諗諗臨時政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0343557d475596080a049fada98943fd5a9ee6","tid":1392851,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:20:10.000Z","msg":"係咪爭司法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0c45eadc51a54596a44e7c321c0267dc65e22f","tid":1392851,"uid":35632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:26:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f694b4384511a5ffa278a4eb7081e4a3597aee21","tid":1392851,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:27:26.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年之前落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年之前！"},{"pid":"8ee849512565185aae3f4395a992ce66f59f7d39","tid":1392851,"uid":43087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:28:42.000Z","msg":"如果打算係5/8罷工既同事可以考慮同HR申請no pay leave<br />\n因為申請No Pay Leave要上醫院管理層批 咁先可以傳到我地既聲音去管理層到<br />\n就算唔批 大家都可以照申請年假<br />\n利申HA HR同事"},{"pid":"8f45d56266392599da0fef44b4bde2b8666d7d00","tid":1392851,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:28:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">老解出兵會否第一時間凍結銀行户口？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dtRugS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dtRugS</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>仲慘過雷曼爆煲！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"e64c1a48f3930588eb2d9c8c2ac32b8dd3b319af","tid":1392851,"uid":181035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:45:34.000Z","msg":"推"}]}